name: Not Your Average Manual Page
author: Bryce
description: Inspired by the manual of Needlessly Complicated Button, the manual itself will do everything* it can to not be able to be read and understood. Instead of a word processing document or an HTML document, the manual is a Snap! project.
notes: *The manual will not be quite as bad as to translate paragraphs into different languages, Atbash, Ceasar, Atbash again, hash, reverse, and whatever (that's too difficult, especially with the hash).
